{"type":null,"faqId":44385,"title":"如何在通话过程中录音？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在通话界面，打开更多选项，点击录音图标，开始录音。再次点击录音图标，结束录音。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=158547\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>录音内容默认存储在“文件管理”的 </span><span class=\"s1\">record</span><span> 文件夹内。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>部分型号的手机不支持通话录音功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=158548\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>在通话过程中，未经对方许可擅自录音可能违反法律法规，请在录音前获取对方的许可。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9885","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400633000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":13,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"通话,录音","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}